<h2 class="pagetitle">Capital Gains Taxation</h2>
<h3 class="pagesubtitle">From <i>The Encyclopedia of Taxation and Tax Policy</i></h3>
<p class="tpcpubauthor">

  <a href="/library/listpubs.cfm?ListAuthors=true&Listpubs=true&AuthorID=7266">Gerald Auten</a> 
</p>






<div id="pubdetailbox"><div id="origdate"> <strong>Published:</strong>&nbsp;October 01, 1999</div> <strong>Availability:</strong><br /> <img src="/images/pdficon.jpg" border=0 alt="">&nbsp;<a href="/UploadedPDF/1000519.pdf" class="smaller">PDF</a>  | <img src="/images/print_friendly.jpg" border=0 alt="">&nbsp;<a href="/publications/urlprint.cfm?ID=1000519" class="smaller">Printer-Friendly Version</a>
